  "content_html": "<div class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"model-response-message-contentr_6195221724e4bb09\">\n<p>काठमाडौँ- जेनजी आन्दोलनले सिंहदरबारभित्रको भवनमा क्षति पुर्याएपछि शिक्षा मन्त्रालयले आफ्ना सेवाहरू अस्थायी रूपमा लैनचौरस्थित केशरमहलबाट सञ्चालन गर्न सुरु गरेको छ।</p>\n<p>भदौ २४ गतेको आन्दोलनका क्रममा शिक्षा मन्त्रालयको भवनमा आगजनी भएपछि उक्त भवन प्रयोग गर्न अयोग्य भएको थियो। सोही कारण मन्त्रालयले केशरमहललाई वैकल्पिक कार्यालयको रूपमा प्रयोग गर्न थालेको हो।</p>\n<p>नवनियुक्त शिक्षा, विज्ञान तथा प्रविधि मन्त्री महावीर पुनले पनि आजै सोही भवनबाट पदभार ग्रहण गर्ने कार्यक्रम रहेको छ। वैज्ञानिक पृष्ठभूमिका पुनलाई शिक्षा मन्त्रीमा सिफारिस गरिएको हो।</p>\n<p><strong>तस्बिरहरूः </strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096936\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113704/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library2.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096935\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113702/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library3.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096934\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113700/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library5.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096933\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113659/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library4.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096931\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113656/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library6.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096930\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113654/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library7.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096929\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113653/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library8.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096928\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113652/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library9.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096927\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113650/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library10.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096926\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113649/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library12.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1096925\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/22113649/education-Ministry_Nepal-photo-library11.jpg\" width=\"2250\" /></p>\n</div>",
